    "description": "<i>Japan, Kyushu Prefecture. 1969<br><br>Rouella Kromowidjojo is a genetic anomaly, a living dialysis machine who can cure almost all forms of disease through the process of crosstransfusion. For the next 15 hours, she will connect with her next patient: the mysterious Rei Fukugawa, whose emaciation and jaundice seem to hide something much more fatal.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015100/extras/693fd16769b7dec7cd7e8b1ca5d80dce.avif?t=1597451414\" width=600 height=171 /></span><br><br><i>Sloth: Heart to Heart</i> is a short and casual Kinetic Visual Novel geared toward Sci-Fi fans. The game romanticizes the medical practice of exchange transfusion to showcase the side effect of a seemingly normal procedure in a seemingly normal pair of characters. Themes include evolutionary psychology, personal obligation, and intersubjectivity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1015100/extras/34690e7fb4567bedb9751ebe3bdf500a.webp?t=1597451414\" width=600 height=31 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong></h2>♥ 3-4 Hours Of Gameplay<br><br>♥ 10+ High Quality CGs<br>♥ 10+ Ambient Soundtrack That Fits In Every Scene<br>♥ 3DCG Backgrounds That Changes Per Scene<br>♥ ...and More.<br><br><br><br>Don't forget to follow our store page!<br><br>Regards,<br>REi",
